Device driver
	write to /dev/mem

Device driver client
	- reads the device 

SM Server
	reading from /dev/mem 
	add the data from /dev/mem into SM
	
SM Client
	read the data from SM
	you can use sockets
	
What is already there?
	- device driver
	    - device name
	- device driver client
	     - device name    
	- SM Server
	   - read the driver values from /dev/mem
	   - put the value to SM
	- SM Client -> no need of change
	
